{"tid":1521088,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[舊聞 - 幫大家打打氣] 國防授權法增懲港官條款","createTime":"2019-08-31T05:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T05:10:48.000Z","uid":78570,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c91fa2f26f3ec2ffe4bca8dc3e4dde2b9e72a504","tid":1521088,"uid":78570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:03:53.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】美國對香港反送中抗爭的發展進一步升溫！美國眾議院與參議院近日先後通過數項《2020年國防授權法案》（National Defense Authorization Act, NDAA）的修訂案，其中參議院版本加入針對侵犯香港人權的個體及組織施加制裁的條文，如兩院最終協商通過條文，美國政府屆時便可「依法」向港府作制裁，包括拒發簽證、經濟制裁及作其他懲罰措施。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190731/20740552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190731%2F20740552&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WkKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=3c65d625\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190731%2F20740552&h=3d476304\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190731/20740552</a>"},{"pid":"6709ac2baacfcd5488ce11a4fec997fdffe80baf","tid":1521088,"uid":78570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"大家話邊個急阿??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBE WATER阿"},{"pid":"3fc6e74f4c5d26cf886f768406f9a1cb56fc7d2f","tid":1521088,"uid":78570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"10月應該會有警隊高層比美國清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src